	   <tr><td colspan=2>Manaburn creates about one point of hate on a mob. You can click Manaburn the second the tank swings the first swing and not get aggro.<br><br>On a side-note, casting the epic causes hate. Was grouping in PoV and was running a bit low on mana, so I clicked on my hourse, swapped on my Mana Robe and clicked my epic to start regenning faster. The minute the epic triggered, the mob aggrod me. It was at half health and I hadn't touched it. This happened about 10 times over the next week, so I gave up on it.<br><br>Now apparently they fixed some aggro issues in PoP with the last patch. They mentioned fixing heal aggro, but I imagine that this was included, as I have yet to have to click my epic in an xp group. Just fair warning that the epic DOES create some hate with a mob.<br>&nbsp;<br>Razormaw Balefire<br>Monk of the 51st Flurry<br><br>Master Branaddar Balefire<br>Wizard of the 62nd Spire<br>Tholuxe Paells<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=286983" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=286983</a></td></tr>
