	   <tr><td colspan=2>I completed my epic during the supposed &quot;bugged&quot; era of the Wizzy Epic. I invised through all the handins and had no problems.<br><br>Invised to hand the oil into the gnome. Invised to give the 3 staves to Arantir. Invised to give the package to the Solomen.<br><br>Yay me on my epic.<br><br>The only problem I've heard of while doing the invis trick is MQing... do NOT attempt to MQ the wiz epic.<br><br>Edit: To do the invis trick, head out to the handins with a non-kos friend who can cast invis on you. Put the item(s) up in the trade window with the NPC, have him cast invis, con the NPC to be sure it's indifferent, then do the handin.<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Sun Jan&nbsp;&nbsp;5 17:53:32 2003</em><br>&nbsp;<br>Razormaw Balefire<br>Monk of the 51st Flurry<br><br>Master Branaddar Balefire<br>Wizard of the 62nd Spire<br>Tholuxe Paells<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=286983" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=286983</a></td></tr>
